dashboard.cc-poetry:
Although the tortoise is alive, there is still time.
Take the snake and take the fog, and finally it is soil.
The old man is screaming, and he is aiming for a thousand miles.
The martyrs are young and strong.
The period of profit and loss is not only in the sky.
The blessing of the good fortune can be won forever.
Fortunately, even swearing, the song is ambiguous.
